{"tid":573852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"個市好好?!【雙屍命案】母子昨午燒炭 大陽擋遮玻璃無人發覺","createTime":"2018-02-27T00:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T02:56:57.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee1a561c1ab693a2668fdb06e92ff882d9601cf","tid":573852,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180227/57879930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57879930&d=zkf9FAfOGufQ6K%2BYQZQLXjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d2a528ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57879930&h=6cdc417b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180227/57879930</a><br />\n<br />\n今晨沙田安耀街一對母子在七人車內燒炭亡，沙田警區(刑事)總督察蕭雯漢表示，兩名死者分別為45歲母親及其9歲兒子，死者丈夫因生意問題，於上月8日在火炭寫字樓吊頸自殺亡，之後女死者一直悶悶不樂，在星期日(25日)女死者返回娘家與家人吃飯，離開後便失去聯絡，直至星期一(26日)中午，娘家親友四出找尋兩母子，至晚上接近凌晨時份(27日)，家人到達馬鞍山輋下村其住所，在屋內發現女死者留下遺書，於是立刻報警，相隔兩個多小時，巡遇警員發現七人車並揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n法醫相信母子死亡時間為(27日)中午，疑因吸入一氧化碳死亡。警方在車內發現一個煮食煲及燒炭痕跡，前後擋風玻璃放有大陽擋，車窗全部關上，兩人在中間座位燒炭，警方翻看附近閉路電視後，發現有行人行經上址，但沒有人留意車內狀況，車上沒有撿獲藥物，亦沒有欠債及家暴記錄。"},{"pid":"721ff3c955220e350ee2ffbb9c857259caad49ea","tid":573852,"uid":86779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"關個市咩事？"},{"pid":"f83423653ad7913923aa63af319bb84d0b0fd2db","tid":573852,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721ff3c955220e350ee2ffbb9c857259caad49ea","tid":573852,"uid":86779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"關個市咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"買左熊"},{"pid":"c5d5d9c275148619e08f7439fe006666903cf718","tid":573852,"uid":5267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b1551a941c84de0369c522686a9b03878ba4df7","tid":573852,"uid":105906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"佢寫男個個因為生意出問題自殺<br />\n佢老婆唔開心 一個月後燒炭<br />\n咁都預示到現時經濟差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}